name: Frankie Franki
description: Perhaps I’m a little old-fashioned, but I like to believe that marriage, for better or for worse is sacred for life. That’s why I am here to find my special one and to build a happy and strong family with him! I am romantic but at the same time I am not up in the clouds. I am honest and I know how to compromise. I can listen and hear. You won’t be bored with me ever as I always will find a way to cheer you up. I am active and like to take good care of myself; to make my body shaped and my mind sharp.
